<title>USA: Calif. Senate panel approves bond investment bill.</title>
<headline>Calif. Senate panel approves bond investment bill.</headline>
<dateline>SACRAMENTO, Calif. 1997-05-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>A California legislative panel on Wednesday approved a bill that would allow many local agencies to invest their bond funds in a broader range of securities.</p>
<p>The Senate Local Government Committee voted 4-to-1 in favor of Senate Bill 1287 by Senator Charles Calderon. The bill now advances to the Senate floor.</p>
